🧠 Sales Prediction Model

A machine learning project that predicts future product sales using historical data and key market features. The model helps businesses make data-driven inventory and marketing decisions by analyzing trends and patterns in sales data.

🚀 Features

Data preprocessing and cleaning of sales datasets

Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) to visualize sales patterns

Implementation of multiple regression algorithms for prediction

Model evaluation using RMSE, R² score, and cross-validation

Interactive visualization of predictions and performance metrics

🛠️ Tools & Technologies

Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Jupyter Notebook

📊 Results

Achieved high prediction accuracy on test data, providing valuable insights into product demand forecasting.
